lead_paragraph: Guinea Bissau is the latest country to upset the established order, overcoming obstacles of conflict, poverty and a lack of infrastructure to reach the African Nations Cup finals.

headline.print_headline: Guinea Bissau Confound Conventional Wisdom to Qualify
